。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;彭博社的新报道&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;即将推出：&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/asKs_JZ2ttqsT7jEuEScMAt9BfxPOG22xiiQp3aFLYE6hTiPMYj1mRT3XYUzAIbnOMq-jd6BJiy54ixBBEp0yHDgOmIv6hsf2inrMIyld5RrwKXM3McOOm2xpaOJl6WrpSzk5lhDoHAMPSXlZsF7v2KsGk-eGjdXxqJ1R5zjnQOemMbkxAKnJYmIoJLwHplEmbzdVDsBsLbHOg5XiYulJicME_4VxG4XqT3BZ8tlb6aZsDnXjmS0P6mvATpPXHPTn9SUqlR8cZMRxI30xACfWUrNJz9JWKgyb9yiG8r0YvKxhm_vR8tgquuNEYKPY4ivwjS1/bxFrCpG6We7AszF04K3LYy64CxAd5iy8/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="今日人工智能"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;获取《今日人工智能》时事通讯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;——通过彭博社全球新闻编辑室的分析，记录人工智能对企业、工人、政府和经济造成的破坏和威胁。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;本周网络公告&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;帕特里克·豪厄尔·奥尼尔 (Patrick Howell O&amp;#39;Neill) 在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/gBbz3HsRFYYCNaBlO5iWB39WG7c6S9vdMGaWA0ASMbky0ypUB9HVVJfv4e5YnpU27ovUqMLBnH8miFkvJCxjBtodejXDesofkaCqDhNu7aRQMYCNNpOY4w-vQxzuw-Z2BhsAzyj-SFeArGuR7msXyk12EsXOD5M-2VdUHQK1dJm4ljYqHHKz36sLR3PKCwEyQeqZx0zhJQwVefuBeQDDp1cVasc5KSD8PWbqgZlonnEoojLdfS5KRbtcVs_dYINK32Mmauk-kZVORMOK4VvholvTpXDfYgM0v-3Wci3nxI4oWaL7O38-XEnYGWB1HDjJX_E2iQ4MroHf-eWyJUEH6Mt62r4FXnudrqBg0tLSMWEpFiE9NHdWP5USSB8jr_lS_MrPlZ9nvIi0LTqYGntyuvNMYu5oWBlwTG78abAxNQfq895c-CiMNjPRzDlk9lGylvHYDJmKs9VrfK4tVVLUZCAXePCkxaI0Am6qJHdlUysNYfioYfYpFm-J06Q80hIM_0BKo4wG_mROcT98fd_oGV6gq-mf7P2KJtdKsx0uVIAyiSVtwSW5eu4/n-gkD9qWjTFfE1u2JXS0DVQWhYoWweA7/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="甚至在 Anthropic 的神话出现之前，人工智能就已经发现了数千个软件缺陷